claudae_analysis.development_pattern: Incremental update to metadata of the training process
claudae_analysis.key_insight: This change adds metadata related to recent examples processed and their categories, providing a better understanding of the training progress.
claudae_analysis.technical_details: The metadata update includes information about the total number of examples, categories (AI integration, testing, data pipeline, and trading), and timestamps.
claudae_analysis.project_impact: This change does not directly affect the overall project functionality but provides valuable context for understanding the AI training progress.
